    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Elevate your drinking experience with these classic whiskey glasses, beautifully crafted for both form and function. With its timeless cut glass design and clear brilliance, this low ball tumbler brings a touch of old school sophistication to modern mixology. Whether you&#039;re enjoying a fine bourbon, a smoky scotch, or crafting the perfect Old Fashioned, these whiskey glass deliver the perfect balance of elegance, weight and comfort in hand. The thick, heavy base ensures stability when mixing and crafting, while enhancing the overall drinking ritual from first to final sip.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Beille 10.82oz Whiskey Glasses Old Fashioned Glass Barware (Many Pack Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>Elevate your drinking experience with these classic whiskey glasses, beautifully crafted for both form and function.</p>\n  <p>With its timeless cut glass design and clear brilliance, this low ball tumbler brings a touch of old school sophistication to modern mixology. Whether you&#039;re enjoying a fine bourbon, a smoky scotch, or crafting the perfect Old Fashioned, these whiskey glass deliver the perfect balance of elegance, weight and comfort in hand. The thick, heavy base ensures stability when mixing and crafting, while enhancing the overall drinking ritual from first to final sip.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>WHISKEY GLASSES:</strong> Inspired by vintage glassware, these classic whiskey glasses add elegance and sophistication to any barware collection; perfect for sipping bourbon, scotch or classic cocktails like an Old Fashioned or Negroni</li>\n    <li><strong>HEAVY BASE FOR STABILITY:</strong> Built with a solid, weighted base to prevent tipping and enhance durability; ideal for muddling ingredients directly in the glass for cocktails that demand precision and presentation</li>\n    <li><strong>VERSATILE 10OZ CAPACITY:</strong> The perfect size for serving whiskey neat, on the rocks, or with mixers; also great for rum, vodka, gin or whiskey and bourbon cocktails, or even non alcoholic beverages</li>\n    <li><strong>GIFTS FOR MEN:</strong> A set of whiskey glasses makes a timeless gift that’s both practical and thoughtful; ideal for birthdays, holidays, anniversaries, Father’s Day, or groomsmen and more; these glasses let him enjoy his favorite bourbon, scotch, or whiskey in style</li>\n    <li><strong>DISHWASHER SAFE:</strong> Designed for everyday convenience, these whiskey glasses are dishwasher safe for quick and effortless cleanup, so you can spend more time enjoying your drink and less time hand washing</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72750/GQj7CkLSk44IuWHiyxgPJnON4w3MtS-metaQkxFX2NhcnZlZF93aGlza2V5X2dsYXNzX21haW5fc2luZ2xlLnBuZw==-.png\" alt=\"Elevate your drinking experience with these classic whiskey glasses, beautifully crafted for both form and function\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> BLE-WHISKGLASS-PARENT</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Clear</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Holding up to 10 ounces, these whiskey glasses are the ideal companion for neat pours, whiskey on the rocks, or a wide variety of stirred cocktails. Durable, dishwasher safe, and a fantastic gift idea for any cocktail enthusiast, these whiskey glasses are a must have addition to any home bar or as an exceptional gift for the whiskey, scotch or bourbon connoisseur.</p>\n  <p>Dishwasher safe.</p>\n  <p>Sold in 2, 4, 6 or 12 packs.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
